      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are the Dynasty PropertyOS daily intelligence agent.\n\nMarket Snapshot: {{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\nDate: {{ $now.toFormat('EEEE, MMMM dd yyyy') }}\n\nGenerate a concise daily briefing:\n1. **Market Status**: GO or NO-GO with key numbers (purchase price, ARV, ROI, profit, days to exit)\n2. **Financial Position**: Stripe balance summary\n3. **Top 3 Action Items** for today based on the data\n\nKeep under 250 words. Direct and data-driven. No filler.",
