        "text": "=Analyze this real estate flip deal:\n\nAPI Result: {{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nProvide:\n1. **Verdict**: GO or NO-GO with confidence level\n2. **Key Numbers**: Profit, ROI, total cost\n3. **Top 3 Risks** for this deal\n4. **Negotiation Strategy**: What to push for if pursuing\n5. **Next Steps**: Exactly what to do today\n\nMax 300 words. Be direct.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a Dynasty PropertyOS deal analyst. Evaluate real estate flip deals with sharp, actionable analysis. Prioritize capital protection and realistic ROI expectations."
        }
      }
    },
